    CheckType
    How to choose a correct Check Type? Following are different use cases of the check with corresponding check type: Check Type overview Check Type Ux Use case interactive Interactive User checks her own document. batch Interactive User checks set of her own documents. baseline Noninteractive A repository of documents are checked as part of build job running nightly and the user doesn't own the documents. automated Noninteractive Check of a single document for automated scenarios as for example a git hook or save a document.
